        Creates an ImageContainer for displaying an image represented by a URI of the form "sqlite://&query=...". Optionally, a set of images represented by SQLite URIs may be browsed.
        Parameters:
        context -
        view -
        imageUID -
        imageURI - The SQLite URI for the image to display.
        imageURIs - Optional set of SQLite URIs for images that may be navigated among. The imageURIs array must include imageURI.
